{"tid":2169204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭國泉向許智峯索取8.2萬元訟費","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T15:00:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"b7014dfa1f197b9bf918d501a1bc8057f56b4c8a","tid":2169204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/K5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FK5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4bbb3292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FK5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ%2F&h=25a0f8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/K5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司長鄭若驊日前再度出手，封殺民主黨立法會議員許智峯向的士司機鄭國泉危險駕駛提出的私人刑事檢控，豁免鄭出席聆訊，被外界批評以人治凌駕法治。據了解，去年被法庭頒佈破產的鄭國泉，隨即透過其代表律師、立法會議員何君堯所屬的律師行，向許智峯索取8.2萬元訟費。有法律界人士指，由於案件被律政司介入，申訴人同樣可追討訟費。"},{"pid":"b87427f22fea3655ead270ba69531afb4d07777e","tid":2169204,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"據悉，在案件中為鄭國泉提出法律援助的何君堯，其所屬的何君柱律師行昨日代表鄭國泉向許智峯發律師信，指由於律政司豁免鄭出席聆訊，根據《裁判官條例》第124條有關「律政司司長介入的案件中有關訟費」，向許追討訟費合共8.2萬元，包括兩名律師收費等，其中何君柱每小時收費9,400元。"},{"pid":"3c41e761a1d233a2471b04863975c9d8ae5892db","tid":2169204,"uid":51701,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"OMDB"},{"pid":"475f693ce1c13ef550c0984006d48d2a62435f2e","tid":2169204,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ca8c47d941dce50bd53c02c1e564c80e72bb9cb","tid":2169204,"uid":118520,"like":13,"dislike":15,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"分化L:泛民冇做野"},{"pid":"54e511e0f9a1d082e0c118208a2c39434c4d9c91","tid":2169204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc